      <description>&lt;p&gt;I started to translate Android mobile mapping application - 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://qfield.org&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;QField&lt;/a&gt; from English to Japanese since September 2019.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I met Mr. Matthias (OpenGIS.ch) at code sprint of FOSS4G 2019 Bucharest, then I got involved QField project. QField is great tool and very much compatible with QGIS. I wish I can constribute to Japan&amp;rsquo;s QGIS community to use it more and more in field.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can see some of my translation from 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://qfield.org/docs/ja/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
